lead_paragraph: The Netherlands' dream Fed Cup run continued as Kiki Bertens crushed Russia's Svetlana Kuznetsova 6-1 6-4 in Moscow on Sunday to send them into the semi-finals of the team competition for the first time since 1997.

headline.print_headline: Dutch Stun Russia to Reach Fed Cup Semis, Czechs Through
